modName: Daenerys Targaryen Alessa Savegame level 1 Breton Riverwood
summary: Level 1 Breton character in Riverwood. Her name is Alessa. She looks like Daenerys Targaryen.
descriptionHtml:
[b][size=15][color=red]Alessa / Daenerys Targaryen[/size][/color][/b]

[b]A savegame of my beautiful character.[/b]

I played around in the character creation kit and suddenly I noticed her likeness to Daenerys Targaryen. I refined her using a couple of photos as my assistance and thus Alessa was created. Rename her to Daenerys if you like ;)

[b][size=10][color=red]Requirements[/size][/color][/b]

If you want to play the savegame itself, you will PROBABLY need these additional mods or you\'ll run into problems.
Requiem + Random Alternate Start
I recommend you instead copy the face from this save via one method or another into your own game.

[b]For her to look like in the screens:[/b]

Install these mods in the following order. Overwhite if prompted. Skip optional steps if you don\'t want her to have a nude body. You also need SKSE (Skyrim Script Extender)

1) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29624/?]Racemenu 1.53[/url] by Expired
2) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29624/?]DisableFaceGenCache 1.1[/url] ((Prevents lag or CTD with Racemenu))
3) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33526/?]ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer 1.3[/url] by kapaer ((Prevents CTD with ApachiiSkyHair))
4) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168]ApachiiSkyHair 1.5[/url] by Apachii
5) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168]ApachiiSkyHairFemale 1.3[/url]
6) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18820]Inhabitants of Skyrim Character Presets[/url] by Rops1981
((OPTIONAL)) 7) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709/?]UNP Dimonized 1.2[/url] by dimon99
((OPTIONAL)) 8) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709/?]UNP 1.51 textures [b]&[/b] UNP HD normal maps[/url]
((OPTIONAL)) 9) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14899/?]UNPB 2.4[/url] by calyps / MrTroubleMaker/xp32/dimon99
10) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3563/?]Coverwomen Look 2 2.0[/url] by mrLenski
11) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3563/?]Coverwomen Look 2 Seamless UNP 2.2[/url] ((Yes, you need both of these Coverwomen files))
12) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/7625/?]Numenume Femalebrows 2.0[/url] by numenume ((The main file))
13) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13722]The Eyes of Beauty Player Unleashed 8.2[/url] by Gabriel Mailhot
14) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30050/?]Sub Surface Full Body Map[/url] by MrTroubleMaker ((Fixes neck seam in most cases))
15) [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/5437/?]Glosstech gloss level 8[/url] by MonoS94 ((Not required, but I think it looks good))

Your ENB or the lack of it will also have a huge effect on how everything ingame looks, including this character. I use Courier\'s Color ENB, personally customized for more performance.

[b][size=10][color=red]Credits[/size][/color][/b]

The Nexus site for providing a repository for Skyrim files.
The modders listed above for their work in making the game even better.
